{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "One group left in May, I think, or April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the other one in August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was not in the one, I was not in the other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But I was working in the mobilization station, so I had access to documents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I stole a document with the-- documents, travel documents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I fill it for myself and 19 others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we got, illegally, to-- on the train and we were travelling towards Krasnoyarsk, which was a harbor on the Caspian Sea, from which transport to Iran were going, of the army and families.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there were family registration in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I had a friend who was later the leader in Israel, one of the leaders of Likud-- Bader, from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he told me to declare myself non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He did the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And he got through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "His-- his cousin was a colonel in the Polish army, baptized.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And Bader got through, he went to Israel and had became one of the top politicians in Israel, the oldest member of the parliament.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to-- when we got to on the train, we came to Ashgabat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we heard there's a Polish mission there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the Polish mission and talked to the colonel in charge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to me, wonderful, you go-- where is your train?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go back to your car, where you are, where is the railway car, and we will send you food and we will take care of you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you know what he did?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He informed the Russian militzia and they came and arrested us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were thrown into jail again on the station of Krasnoyarsk railway station.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
